{"tid":384447,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄺美雲斥球迷噓國歌懶型 籲照鏡認命    感恩做中國人","createTime":"2017-09-02T10:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T10:03:08.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"030c92f11c2b7dd322f272a3ef8efd683a6ccd40","tid":384447,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504341340_d127.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504341340_d127.png&h=96f642d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大常委會周五通過《國歌法》草案，於10月1日起實施，並會通過《基本法》以本地立法形式引入香港。江西政協、本港前藝人鄺美雲為梁粉網媒《港人講地》拍片護航，批評噓國歌的球迷不尊重國歌，「有啲人鍾意反叛，或者覺得咁樣幾有型，總之我就同你唔一樣&hellip;&hellip;我唔知呢啲係咩心態」，但「點樣唔一樣，你照下鏡，你係中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然新民黨立法會議員葉劉淑儀笑言「我都係用廣東話唱（國歌）咋喎&hellip;&hellip;喺香港」，但鄺美雲批評有人「你自己國歌你都唔唱好，你想唱咩國歌呢？你唱人哋嗰隻，係咪先？」鄺聲言，不尊重國歌，亦即不尊重國家、不尊重自己，「我想話畀大家聽，尊重自己嘅身份，尊重自己係一個中國人，你要感恩呢樣嘢囉」。"},{"pid":"581fbbb7800e43519398513fde1f4e70bdc720bb","tid":384447,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"聽到英國國歌起立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0498102b07d801875a1f8ba5db214bb8118cbd25","tid":384447,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:02:36.000Z","msg":"連登仔到時港獨實會清算佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（如果成功）"},{"pid":"cd05f7036f47a2f3085538a6ef832bedae8e714c","tid":384447,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"黨國不分如何愛國"}